About this item

  • Unbreakable Container The large container is featured with unbreakable plastic for long lasting usage.
  • Anti Skid Base The veggie cutter is very easy to use and is featured with a non-skid base for the effortless use and satisfying results.
  • Fastest and Safest It is one of the fastest, safest and easiest way to chop or dice fruits and vegetables. It is effortless to use.
  • Stainless Steel Blade The blades are made up of premium quality stainless steel for smooth chopping. For easy chopping, the blades are sharp and pyramid shaped.
  • Easy to Clean and Store The chopper comes with advanced push button which ensures easy and hygienic cleaning. The container can also be used to store vegetable and fruits in refrigerator.
  • Variants in Blades The chopper comes with different kind of blades for variations in chopping and dicing. It also comes with a peeler with sharp stainless steel blade.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
